--------------------------------------------------------------------
                Requirements
--------------------------------------------------------------------
ocaml
menhir

--------------------------------------------------------------------
                Make options
--------------------------------------------------------------------
make            build fsafe project
make opt        build fsafe project (native)
make depend     calculate dependencies
make graph      build callgraph pdf file
make clean      remove binaries and obj files of project.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
                Fsafe options
--------------------------------------------------------------------
-v              verbose mode
-d              debug_mode
-i              interpretor
-t              terminator
